      "description": "Hi everyone! I\u2019m so excited to share this absolute gem with you. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it was brand new! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept in a garage and pampered. Not a single scratch or smudge to be found\u2014it\u2019s just perfect. It drives like a dream and I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
