      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a true survivor-grade specimen. This vehicle features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, with the VANOS system recently overhauled and the rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its factory-spec damping and lateral stiffness. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-Differential lock. Every body panel retains its original VIN tag and factory-applied finish, showing zero signs of thermal cycling or oxidation. This is a mechanically synchronized, collector-quality example for the enthusiast who demands a zero-compromise driving experience.",
